    Refactor architecture: Introduce out-of-core Rust CLI tools (bucketer & packer)
    
    - Refactored src/lib.rs to remove stateful Table Functions, keeping only pure mathematical scalar UDFs (hilbert_xy and hilbert_normalized) to leverage DuckDB's SIMD and zero-copy Arrow memory.
